<L>__{exterior pier 13. day.}
<A>__{truman comes back to reality. he steels himself, shuts out the doubts and dives into the water.}
<L>__{exterior new york harbor. day.}
<A>__{underwater we see truman panicking at the shock of the cold sea, arms and legs flailing. suddenly he stops and sinks for a moment in the weight of his clothes. then slowly he rises to the surface and begins to swim. moored in the harbor is the scaled down replica of columbus' flagship, the santa maria.}
